{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e15dd0d974","title":"给李立三“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"694187a2cd","index":0,"year":1929,"month":11,"day":28,"articleId":"e15dd0d974"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"5423e55f17","name":"李立三","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji4-1","name":"毛泽东全集第4卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji4-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji4-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3207885e0e","type":"paragraph","text":"给李立三“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"af7f19c138","type":"paragraph","text":"（1929年11月28日）立三兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"85ef05f04b","type":"paragraph","text":"多久不和你通讯了，陈毅同志来才知道你的情形。我大病三个月，现虽好了，但精神未全复元。开慧和岸英等我时常念及他们，想和他们通讯，不知通信处。闻说泽民在上海，请兄替我通知泽民，要他把开慧的通信处告诉我，并要他写信给我","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"00222583fb","type":"paragraph","text":"我知识荒到十分，请你时常寄书报给我，能抽暇写信指导无幸。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"a25edf419e","type":"paragraph","text":"独秀近来行动“真点有此理，中央的驳议文件已经到此，我们当普遍地宣传。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"d703cba00f","type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义的敬礼","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"4fab8abfdd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东邮政通信处“","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"f52197a069","type":"paragraph","text":"151","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"8409300989","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]李立三（1899—1967），湖南融陵人，当时任中共中央政治局常委、中央宣传部部长。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"6cd8ef707c","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]开慧，即杨开慧（1901—1930），湖南长沙人，毛泽东的夫人，1921年加入中国共产党。岸英，即毛岸英，毛泽东的长子。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"bafc864062","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]泽民，即毛泽民（1896—1943），湖南湘潭人，毛泽东之弟，当时负责中共中央出版部的工作。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"bae613de3c","type":"paragraph","text":"14]指陈独秀当时在党内散布托派观点，成立小组织等反党活动。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"e06b71bb0a","type":"paragraph","text":"现在保存的此信的抄件中，引号内空缺。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"},{"id":"56a6c4819c","type":"paragraph","text":"古田会议前夕，毛泽东亲自领导红军在福建连城县新泉村进行整顿。毛泽东亲自深入部队调查研究，为召开古田会议作好准备。毛泽东在新泉村的住地“望云草室”","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974"}],"page":{"id":"81f814aeee","publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"e15dd0d974","start":292,"end":294}}}},"__N_SSG":true}